node.text: I legit can’t believe I was able to achieve this blonde look using @orscurlsunleashed temporary hair wax!! My curls are popping and I refuse to bleach my hair again so this is a HIT!!! It washes right out and left my hair so soft and bouncy! @orscurlsunleashed #CUcolorblast

node.text: Happy Birthday Daddy! Thank you for being the best Daddy a girl could ask for. Always there to support me. Every softball game, coming to see me at work at my first job, taking me off to college, letting me practice on you in the kitchen when I first started tattooing, and right here at the grand opening of my shop. You’ve never missed a beat. 3 things you’ve always told us growing up, “I’ll always love you, I’ll always take care of you, and I’ll never let anything bad happen to you” And you meant that! We love you so much! @jken
